pd_0_com_0text: Hey! watch where you’re going, freak!
pd_1_com_0text: Don't be so mean! You bumped into me.
pd_1_com_2text: Didn't you're mom teach you how to walk?!
pd_2_com_0text: Don't blame me, it's your fault!
pd_6_com_0text: Whatever, you made me look like a fool...
pd_7_com_0text: No Jannet, I just won against you, taht's it.
pd_7_com_1text: Look, you have always been so mean to me...
pd_7_com_2text: not only me but to others too...
pd_7_com_3text: being mean to people won't make you strong...
pd_7_com_4text: or it won't make you look cool...
pd_7_com_5text: You just make people around you upset, that's it!
pd_7_com_6text: In the end, you will find yourself being upset just like this...
pd_8_com_0text: I always thought I would be cool if I acted that way...
pd_9_com_0text: ...and, do you think you look cool now?
pd_9_com_1text: sorry but, acting that way ruins other people's lives,
pd_10_com_1text: You were the good girl and you won!
pd_11_com_0text: No, look we are all friends...
